message: "If you use these skills, please cite them as below."
title: "academic-book-skills"
abstract: >-
  Book-production skills for writing, structuring and typesetting academic textbooks and
  monographs in LaTeX — chapter structure and box/case numbering, a numbering/cross-reference
  consistency audit, source & citation verification with a reproducible audit ledger, and
  front/back-matter, cover and print-quality support.
type: software
version: 0.7.5
date-released: 2026-07-13
license: MIT
